  <description><![CDATA[<p>With ski-in, ski-out access to Blackcomb Mountain, the Blackcomb Spring Suites offers incredible skiing opportunities in a traditional Canadian Lodge style of accommodation.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #e23333;">Save up to 25% when you book by 19th April 2025</span> </strong></p>
<p><strong><em>(See added value section below)</em></strong></p>
<h2>Ski-in / Ski-out</h2>
<p>Blackcomb Springs Suites offers perfect ski-in and ski-out access of the Blackcomb Mountain. It's located right on the side of the mountain with its own slopeside entrance, providing you an effortless start to the day.</p>
<p>Blackcomb Village is a five minute drive or ski away, and a frequent complimentary shuttle bus runs all day to and from <a data-udi="umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0c45d07f55a64313a6e4bc714b58b52d}" title="Whistler">Whistler</a> Village. You'll have all the benefits of being a little further from the centre in a quiet location, while still being well connected to the hustle and bustle of the village.</p>
<h2>Canadian Lodge Style</h2>
<p>As you walk through the front doors you'll feel like you have just stepped into a real wilderness lodge. This carries throughout the hotel's public areas with all the amenities and comforts of a modern hotel.</p>
<p>The outdoor pool and hot tubs are slopeside and offer great views of the surroundings.</p>
<h2>Amenities</h2>
<p>Blackcomb Springs has a wide range of room types and all the amenities you need for your stay. Each studio and suite comes with a fully-equipped kitchen, lounge and fireplace. There is also an on-site mini-mart and laundry machines.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
