  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studios </strong>are open concept rooms at 42m² and comfortably sleep up to three adults with a Queen bed and Queen sized sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>One Bedroom Suites</strong> are 54m² and have a separate bedroom with King size bed. These rooms can sleep up to four using a Queen sofa bed in the living area. These are also available with a slope side view, available at a supplement. </p>
<p><strong>Two Bedroom Suites </strong>are 80m² and have two separate bedrooms and two bathroom suites. With a King size bed in the master bedroom, Twin beds or double bunk beds in the second bedroom, and a Queen sofa bed in the living area, these suites are suitable for up to six guests.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bath / shower combo</li>
<li>Full equipped kitchen</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Fireplace</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Tea / coffee making facilities </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
